OL,3,C'Life-saving' inflatable cushion
OL,4,Ccreated to safely move patients
OL,6,FA team of academics in Bath have
OL,7,Fcreated a device to help move
OL,8,Fcritically ill patients.
OL,10,FThe 'BathMat' is an inflatable device
OL,11,Fcreated to help doctors and nurses
OL,12,Fsafely move patients.
OL,14,FThe device is set to enter clinical
OL,15,Ftrials at the Royal United Hospitals
OL,16,FBath NHS Foundation Trust (RUH).
OL,18,FIt was designed by engineers at the
OL,19,FUniversity of Bath in collaboration
OL,20,Fwith doctors at the RUH.
