OL,3,C'Life-saving' inflatable cushion
OL,4,Ccreated to safely move patients
OL,6,FThe 'BathMat' is a flat balloon-like
OL,7,Fcushion made to assist healthcare
OL,8,Fstaff move the most critically ill
OL,9,Fpatients.
OL,11,FDr Andy Georgiou has been the
OL,12,Fconsultant lead for the project since
OL,13,Fthe outset.
OL,15,FHe said: "Turning some patients who
OL,16,Fare sedated and on a ventilator onto
OL,17,Ftheir front is life-saving.
OL,26,@wD@JOU
