PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F436A1721043650
OL,3,C'Life-saving' inflatable cushion
OL,4,Ccreated to safely move patients
OL,6,F"Caring for these patients whilst on
OL,7,Ftheir front is challenging but vital
OL,8,Fto avoid causing the patient serious
OL,9,Finjury.
OL,11,F"This device has three main benefits:
OL,12,Fimproving safety for our sickest
OL,13,Fpatients, releasing staff to care for
OL,14,Fother critically ill patients and
OL,15,Freducing the risk of injury to our
OL,16,Fspecialist teams of staff.
OL,18,F"I look forward to the trial which
OL,19,Fwill help us to better quantify these
OL,20,Fbenefits".
