OL,3,C'Life-saving' inflatable cushion
OL,4,Ccreated to safely move patients
OL,6,FCritically ill patients on the
OL,7,Fintensive care unit who are sedated
OL,8,Fand on a ventilator with severe lung
OL,9,Finjury, can benefit from being placed
OL,10,Fon their front.
OL,12,FThis can increase the oxygen levels in
OL,13,Ftheir blood and reduces their risk of
OL,14,Fdeath by up to 17%.
OL,16,FTo avoid painful bed sores and
OL,17,Finjuries to other parts of the body,
OL,18,Fnational guidelines require these
OL,19,Fpatients to be repositioned every two
OL,20,Fto four hours.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
