OL,3,C'Life-saving' inflatable cushion
OL,4,Ccreated to safely move patients
OL,6,FCurrently, this is done using sliding
OL,7,Fsheets or hoists, with repositioning
OL,8,Faccounting for over half a million
OL,9,Fstaff hours per year in the NHS.
OL,11,FThe researchers behind the device say
OL,12,Fthey hope it will make it possible for
OL,13,Fjust two staff to complete the
OL,14,Fprocess, and cut the time needed from
OL,15,Fover half an hour per position
OL,16,Fadjustment to less than 10 minutes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
