OL,3,C'Life-saving' inflatable cushion
OL,4,Ccreated to safely move patients
OL,6,FWhilst substantially improving the
OL,7,Fsafety of the procedure for patients,
OL,8,Fand releasing staff to perform other
OL,9,Fcare duties, it also has the potential
OL,10,Fto reduce the risk of manual handling
OL,11,Finjuries for staff.
OL,13,FCurrently, 16,500 patients are cared
OL,14,Ffor in this way in the NHS each year.
OL,15,FA device like this could reduce the
OL,16,Flikelihood of pressure sores and organ
OL,17,Finjury, potentially allowing for more
OL,18,Ffrequent repositioning.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
