OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F436A1721043650
OL,3,C'Life-saving' inflatable cushion
OL,4,Ccreated to safely move patients
OL,6,FThe device could bring knock-on
OL,7,Fbenefits such as freeing up staff to
OL,8,Fperform other duties and protecting
OL,9,Fstaff-to-patient ratios.
OL,11,FDr Alexander Lunt, leading the project
OL,12,Ffrom the University of Bath, said:
OL,13,F"Our goal is that the device will be
OL,14,Fproven to maintain or improve safety
OL,15,Fstandards and enhance patient outcomes
OL,16,Fin the most unwell patients.
OL,18,F"We aim to achieve this while saving
OL,19,Ftime and reducing the number of
OL,20,Fclinicians required needed to
OL,21,Freposition prone patients.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
