OL,3,C'Life-saving' inflatable cushion
OL,4,Ccreated to safely move patients
OL,6,F"The device has been carefully
OL,7,Fdeveloped as a close collaboration
OL,8,Fover the past two years.
OL,10,F"We have received regular feedback
OL,11,Ffrom clinicians and patients alike,
OL,12,Fbeing described as a game changer and
OL,13,Fno-brainer by independent reviewers."
