OL,3,C'Life-saving' inflatable cushion
OL,4,Ccreated to safely move patients
OL,6,FAfter receiving Research Capability
OL,7,Ffunding from the RUH, as well as
OL,8,Ffunding from the University's Impact
OL,9,FAcceleration Account, the project has
OL,10,Fnow received #357,000 from the
OL,11,FNational Institute of Health and Care
OL,12,FResearch (NIHR) to determine the
OL,13,Feffectiveness of the device and to
OL,14,Fexplore its commercial potential.
OL,16,FThe clinical trial will begin in late
OL,17,F2024 and run for 14 months, taking
OL,18,Fplace at the RUH as well as other NHS
OL,19,Ftrusts in the UK.
